narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I became more acquainted to the Cervantess masterpiece through the thorough analysis provided by the professors lectures. Also, the four essays That were required from ya to write further deepened my interest in the novel.
The course allowed me to read the novel from a new perspective. It helped me improve my reading and interpretation skills and to understand plenty of the subjects the book exposes.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The main strength was the fact we could read the novel in its original language, Spanish. I think that was very helpful for English-speakers students.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would certainly do. Prof. Gonzlez Echevarra is a world renowned Quijote scholar, and being able to get acquainted with his wonderful insights and ways of making scholarship is an invaluable experience.
Yes, I would definitely recommend this course.
